These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, mirinda, almond-milk
3 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, rat
1. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the person drinking water and the owner of the ferret##7
2. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
3. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | mirinda | water |
| Pet           | ferret  | rat     | bird  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-2::.
3 different pets are kept: frog, rat, horse
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, tram, van
1. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the frog is somewhere between the owner of the horse and the person driving the tram##7
3. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |
| Pet   | rat | frog | horse |
| Transport     | tram       | van     | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, photographer, teacher
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, subway, train
1. the person driving the subway is somewhere between the project-manager and the person driving the roller##7
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the photographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |   3    |
| Job    | project-manager | photographer | teacher  |
| Transport   | train  | subway  | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, scientist, teacher
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, tulip, daffodil
1. the project-manager is somewhere between the person who growsdaffodil and the scientist##7
2. the person who growstulip is not the project-manager##6
3. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere to the right of the person who growstulip##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |      3      |
| Job           | scientist | project-manager | teacher     |
| Flower   | tulip    | begonia          | daffodil |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-5::.
City: paris, hamburg, marseilles
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, skateboard
1. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere between the person driving the skateboard and the person traveling to hamburg##7
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| City   | paris      | marseilles     | hamburg   |
| Transport     | skateboard | quad-bike | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-6::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, balloon-flower, daffodil
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, japanese, pakistani
1. the colombian is on the left or right of the japanese##3
2. the japanese is somewhere to the left of the colombian##5
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the pakistani##1
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere between the pakistani and the person who growsrose##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Flower   | daffodil    | balloon-flower     | rose     |
| Nationality   | pakistani | japanese | colombian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, documentary, time-travel
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere between the person watching mystery movies and the person who's sport is badminton##7
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Movie-Genre     | time-travel       | documentary      | mystery       |
| Sport   | badminton | skateboarding | basketball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-8::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, electrician, entrepreneur
3 different games are played: bridge, scrabble, go
1. the person playing go is on the left or right of the doctor##3
2. the person playing bridge is somewhere between the person playing go and the electrician##7
3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Job           | entrepreneur | doctor  | electrician |
| Game   | go      | bridge | scrabble      |

