.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, writing
City: prague, marseilles, colone
1. the person traveling to colone is not the person who's hobby is writing##6
2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person traveling to prague is somewhere between the person traveling to marseilles and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | writing | chess   |
| City     | colone    | prague  | marseilles |

