.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, milk, sprite
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, strawberry, watermelon
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person eating watermelon is the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person eating strawberry##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | milk   | sprite    | coffee |
| Food      | watermelon | raspberry | strawberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-11::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, rock-climbing, traveling
House: craftsman, townhouse, wooden
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere between the townhouse house and the craftsman house##7
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the craftsman house is not the person who's hobby is traveling##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | traveling | fishing | rock-climbing |
| House   | townhouse    | wooden    | craftsman         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-12::.
There 3 different types of food: lemon, onion, plum
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, rat, hamster
1. the owner of the rat is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the owner of the rat and the person eating lemon##7
3. the person eating onion is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food          | lemon  | plum       | onion     |
| Pet   | hamster | goldfish | rat |

