2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person eating banana##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person eating artichoke##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food        | banana | watermelon | artichoke |
| Sport   | ice-hockey  | snowboarding       | weightlifting      |

