.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-15::.
3 different pets are kept: bird, mouse, turtle
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, november, january
1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere between the owner of the turtle and the person who's birthday is in november##7
3. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Pet     | turtle  | bird       | mouse    |
| Birthday   | may | january | november |

