.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-16::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, electronic, d&b
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, pakistani, thai
1. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the right of the fan of d&b##5
2. the fan of d&b is the fan of d&b##1
3. the fan of electronic is somewhere between the thai and the malaysian##7
4. the malaysian is the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre          | d&b | electronic     | ambient   |
| Nationality   | thai   | pakistani | malaysian |

